Creating a Map 4

·        Double click on the State in Dimension.

·        Automatically Latitude and Longitude appear on the Row and Column Shelf.

·        Similarly, State appears in Detail.


·        Change the Map from Automatic to Filled Map in Marks Card


        ·   The map Below will appear.

            


    ·        Drag and Drop State in Label


    ·        Drag and Drop Revenue in Color so that Revenue by State  is displayed in different colors.

     


  ·        Change the Measure from Sum to Average

     

 

  ·    Right Click on Revenue and then Drag and Drop it in Label.

  ·    Drop Field Dialog Box will Pop Up. Then Click on Avg(Revenue) then Click OK.   

     

   ·   Then Format the Avg(Revenue)  by Clicking on Drop-Down of Avg(Revenue) in Label.

   


·   In Pane, Click on Numbers - - - > Currency (Custom) - - - > Decimal to 0.


·   Adding the Title by Right Clicking on Sheet 1.


·   Customize the Title by adding Colors and Changing the font.
